---
title: Ghoulish Goulash with Pork, Beetroot and Dill
description: Our Halloween goulash is guaranteed to be a monster hit. Pork mince is seasoned with hot chilli powder, smokey paprika, grated beetroot and chopped tomatoes for a thick sauce that tastes spooktacularly good. Served on top of thick pappardelle ribbons (perfect for mopping up the sauce) with a dollop of sour cream and sprinkling of dill, this dish is truly wicked. Happy Halloween!
